      "description": "Raw force-displacement data and derived QoIs (stiffness, yield force, force at 40 mm displacement) from N=11 non-cannulated 7.5 mm pedicle screw constructs tested at two independent laboratories under ASTM F1717 static compression-bending protocol. Data were collected and locked prior to the November 2025 mesh-density revision; the modelling team assessed the revision as not material to the experimental dataset's applicability, as only the FEA discretization scheme — not the boundary conditions or load application — was updated. Formal re-validation against the revised model build was not performed.",
      "dataVintage": "2025-10-10T00:00:00Z"
