      "name": "Ti-6Al-4V ELI material property database — pedicle screw alloy",
      "description": "Elastic modulus, yield strength, and ultimate tensile strength values for Ti-6Al-4V ELI rod and screw stock, sourced from certificate-of-conformance testing of the production lot used in bench testing. Values were incorporated into the FEA model as isotropic linear-elastic material cards. The dataset predates the November 2025 model revision; the team noted that material cards were unchanged in the revision and therefore treated this dataset as current without formal re-qualification.",
      "dataVintage": "2025-10-14T00:00:00Z"
    }
